il.ac.technion.nlp.nli.parser

Class InstructionKnowledgeGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.nlp.sempre.KnowledgeGraph
      • il.ac.technion.nlp.nli.parser.InstructionKnowledgeGraph

  • public class InstructionKnowledgeGraph
extends edu.stanford.nlp.sempre.KnowledgeGraph
    A GraphKb wrapper with required logic for integration into Sempre. Unless specified otherwise, when referring to a NameValue id we mean one without a preceding "!" (that indicates a reversed relation). When we want to refer to ids that may contain a preceding "!" we use the term "reversible id".
